# Cloudflare Pages proxy rules — status 200 makes these transparent proxies
# (not browser redirects), so the frontend's existing fetch('/auth/...') and
# fetch('/api/...') calls keep working unchanged and stay same-origin from
# the browser's point of view. The Railway backend URL below must match the
# deployed backend exactly.
/auth/*  https://peanuts-pets-production.up.railway.app/auth/:splat  200
/api/*   https://peanuts-pets-production.up.railway.app/api/:splat   200
